title: Interview and photo essay - Gareth McGuigan
text:
Interview and photo essay - Gareth McGuigan Christina Pfeiffer | 6th Jul 2015 5:23 PM Christina Pfeiffer Queensland photo essay. Photo: Gareth McGuigan Popular Stories Cars For Sale 
Southeast Queensland photographer Gareth McGuigan - interview and photographs. McGuigan, who lives in Bahrs Scrub has a wonderful portfolio of photographs snapped around Southeast Queensland. From Mount Barney in the Scenic Rim to the Gold Coast. His most memorable moment is photographing Lamington National Park. Check out this fantastic photo essay of Southeast Queensland . It will remind you how lucky we are to live in this part of the world.
